</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PUTIN-MEDIA-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PUTIN AND THE PRESS: AN INVITATION YOU CAN'T REFUSE _ BE ON MY
TEAM 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
special arrangement only. Asian and European points: contact Karl
