   FBN-COWBOYS _ Previewing the Dallas vs. San Francisco NFL game.
Now that Dallas has won its first game, the Cowboys seek
consistency. The next test is the once-powerful San Francisco
49ers. (Cantu, Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
<P>
   AUTO RACING
</P>
<P>
   COXNET INSIDE NASCAR 0921: HELMET SUPPORT -- Two fatal crashes
at New Hampshire International Speedway and injuries to drivers at
other NASCAR Winston Cup tracks have created a large demand for a
head-and-neck support device known by the acronym HANS.
</P>
<P>
   The device, made of carbon fiber and kevlar, has a high-back
collar and straps that fit under a driver's shoulder belts. It also
has straps that attach to the back of the driver's helmet. In a
sudden impact, the straps limit the forward movement of the
driver's head.
</P>
<P>
   Sudden forward movement of the driver's head causes the type of
injuries that killed Adam Petty and Kenny Irwin. (Minter, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). Art includes a graphic showing how the HANS
system works.
</P>
