<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-23 14:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8895 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-OLY-ARATON-COLUMN-NYT     09-23 0842
