<HEADLINE>
A GRUNT AS PRESIDENT? HISTORY SALUTES A FEW GOOD MEN 
</HEADLINE>
   (The Week in Review)  
 (EDS:  changes `three' to `four' in 3rd graf ) 
(NOTE TO INTERNATIONAL CLIENTS: For international clients' use by
