<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-23 17:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8976 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-DEL-REAL-645(2TAKES)-     09-23 0701
