FBC-UCLA-OREGON (Eugene, Ore.) _ UCLA loses to Oregon 29-10. 
By Billy Witz. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
FBC-UCLASIDE (Euegene, Ore.) _ UCLA sidebar. 
By Billy Witz. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
