   6. HIGH TIDE, by Jude Deveraux. (Pocket Books, $7.99.)
</P>
<P>
   A New York businesswoman, on a trip to the Everglades,
</P>
<P>
   becomes a suspect in a murder case.
</P>
<P>
   7. BLACK NOTICE, by Patricia Cornwell. (Berkley, $7.99.)
</P>
