   8. NIGHT SHIELD, by Nora Roberts. (Intimate Moments/
</P>
<P>
   Silhouette, $4.50.) A police officer tries to stop
</P>
<P>
   herself from falling for a good-looking shady
</P>
<P>
   character.
</P>
